      <title>新任北约秘书长吕特首次出访基辅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/new-nato-chief-rutte-makes-kyiv-his-first-foreign-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·吕特抵达基辅，开始作为北约新任秘书长的首次出访，以表达对乌克兰在反抗俄罗斯入侵的第三年战争中给予的支持，并表示将把增加武器生产作为优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/new-nato-chief-rutte-makes-kyiv-his-first-foreign-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
